title: Deep Star Six
description:
Movie Description
Far below the surface, the crew of DeepStar Six is on a mission to establish a navy base on the ocean floor--until they unwittingly disturb an undersea monster. Inspired by classic 1950s B-monster movies and directed by Sean S. Cunningham (director of the original FRIDAY THE 13TH), DEEPSTAR SIX is a watery nod to the man versus monster genre.

Credits 
Cast: Taurean Blacque 
Director: Sean Cunningham
